overview: Fairuz had to work overtime to raise money to cover the spending for Aidilfitri. In Fairuz's family tradition, family members often list items of what they want for Aidilfitri and this year, the list is longer and more expensive. To avoid disappointment his family, Fairuz worked extra hard and told his employees to work overtime to achieve the company's goals until Fairuz is stressed out.
title: Senarai Raya Papa
